<MELItem itemNbr="21-45-05" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-45-05.1.2-21-45-05">
<Title>Zonal Duct Heaters</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate inoperative heater (AMM DDG 21-45-05).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For zone A1 heater inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open circuit breaker HEATER-CABIN 	ZONE A and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to zone A1 heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to zone A1 heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For zone B1 heater inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-CABIN ZONE B ELEMENT 1</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-CABIN ZONE B ELEMENT 2</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to zone B1 heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to zone B1 heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>